15
00:01:10,350 --> 00:01:10,870
All right.

16
00:01:11,400 --> 00:01:13,480
I still need to go back
to take care of my father, after all.

17
00:01:14,560 --> 00:01:15,510
The order is from Mr. Jin.

18
00:01:15,790 --> 00:01:16,950
I heard it's quite a significant amount.

19
00:01:17,430 --> 00:01:19,870
It would be great
if we could sign the deal with them.

20
00:01:22,120 --> 00:01:23,760
I heard Mr. Jin of Nancheng

21
00:01:23,760 --> 00:01:25,000
needs a supply of timber urgently.

22
00:01:25,000 --> 00:01:25,920
A large amount of timber.

23
00:01:26,480 --> 00:01:28,590
If you can take that order,

24
00:01:28,790 --> 00:01:29,680
maybe you'll be able

25
00:01:29,680 --> 00:01:31,310
to establish a partnership with Mr. Jia.

26
00:01:32,840 --> 00:01:33,950
Is this news from a reliable source?

27
00:01:34,590 --> 00:01:35,680
Of course.

28
00:01:35,680 --> 00:01:37,510
I heard the news from a friend.

29
00:01:43,710 --> 00:01:44,070
All right.

30
00:01:44,920 --> 00:01:46,000
I'll look into it.

31
00:01:47,040 --> 00:01:49,150
If I manage to secure the deal,

32
00:01:49,790 --> 00:01:51,430
you'll be rewarded for your contribution.

33
