(You're still such a fool, Ye Qinglan.)

34
00:01:57,950 --> 00:02:00,000
(There's no way
I would let you get credit for this.)

35
00:02:03,510 --> 00:02:04,920
I didn't expect

36
00:02:05,070 --> 00:02:05,920
to get

37
00:02:05,920 --> 00:02:07,680
such a big order for timber so soon.

38
00:02:08,400 --> 00:02:09,080
An auspicious start to the business.

39
00:02:09,080 --> 00:02:10,080
It's a good sign.

40
00:02:10,400 --> 00:02:12,120
With you at the helm,

41
00:02:12,120 --> 00:02:13,080
the Mu Family will surely prosper.

42
00:02:15,120 --> 00:02:16,870
If it weren't for the late madam

43
00:02:16,870 --> 00:02:18,280
who used to get in my way,

44
00:02:18,800 --> 00:02:20,470
this family wouldn't have gone

45
00:02:20,560 --> 00:02:22,360
into decline now.

46
00:02:24,080 --> 00:02:24,400
The son

47
00:02:24,400 --> 00:02:26,400
of the richest man in Shanghai, Mr. Tang,
has recently come to Jiangcheng.

48
00:02:27,120 --> 00:02:29,310
I heard that Young Master Tang
has strong political

49
00:02:29,310 --> 00:02:30,080
and business connections.

50
00:02:30,750 --> 00:02:32,400
He's planning to do a big business in Jiangcheng,

51
00:02:32,870 --> 00:02:34,430
and he's currently looking for partners.

52
00:02:36,960 --> 00:02:38,030
Where is he staying now?

53
00:02:39,000 --> 00:02:39,910
Send an invitation to him immediately.

54
00:02:40,280 --> 00:02:41,280
I want to meet him.

55
00:02:42,560 --> 00:02:43,430
Rumor has it

56
00:02:43,430 --> 00:02:44,560
that he has an odd temper.

57
00:02:44,960 --> 00:02:46,030
He is very picky.

58
00:02:46,120 --> 00:02:47,430
He tried out all the inns in Jiangcheng.

59
00:02:47,750 --> 00:02:49,000
None of them could satisfy him.

60
00:02:49,240 --> 00:02:49,960
I heard he is looking

61
00:02:49,960 --> 00:02:50,910
to rent his own residence now.

62
00:02:53,710 --> 00:02:55,150
This is a good opportunity for us.

63
00:02:56,150 --> 00:02:57,560
He won't find

64
00:02:57,910 --> 00:02:59,120
a more magnificent residence

65
00:02:59,150 --> 00:03:00,430
than the Mu's Residence in all of Jiangcheng.

66
00:03:05,800 --> 00:03:06,870
Tell Wang to advise Mu Ancheng

67
00:03:06,870 --> 00:03:08,520
to take the water route

68
00:03:08,680 --> 00:03:10,240
to ensure the goods arrive on time.

69
00:03:10,800 --> 00:03:11,560
Yes.

70
00:03:19,180 --> 00:03:23,900
[Mu's Residence]

71
00:03:34,310 --> 00:03:36,280
Welcome to the Mu's Residence, Young Master Tang.

72
00:03:51,960 --> 00:03:55,680
It's a pleasure to meet you, First Young Master Mu.

73
00:03:57,030 --> 00:03:58,800
(Mu Anhe?)

74
00:04:06,560 --> 00:04:07,080
Mr. Mu.

75
00:04:07,470 --> 00:04:07,870
What's the matter?

76
00:04:08,150 --> 00:04:09,240
Is Young Master Tang not welcome here?

77
00:04:10,800 --> 00:04:11,630
Not at all.

78
00:04:13,560 --> 00:04:15,120
I've heard a lot about you.

79
00:04:16,190 --> 00:04:17,310
I finally get to meet you today.

80
00:04:18,000 --> 00:04:19,120
You're in your prime

81
00:04:19,360 --> 00:04:20,310
and your presence is extraordinary.

82
00:04:20,630 --> 00:04:22,120
Even I, as a man, am impressed.

83
00:04:25,830 --> 00:04:28,480
(Can two people that look so alike
actually exist in this world?)

84
00:04:36,680 --> 00:04:38,800
(Mu Anhe? He isn't dead?)

85
00:04:41,270 --> 00:04:45,000
(Are you Mu Anhe or Tang Zifeng?)

86
00:04:48,800 --> 00:04:49,950
Who is he?

87
00:04:50,480 --> 00:04:51,310
Why does he look…

88
00:04:53,270 --> 00:04:56,630
This is the Third Young Master
of the Tang Family in Shanghai.

89
00:04:56,800 --> 00:04:57,870
Tang Zifeng.

90
00:04:58,830 --> 00:04:59,950
He is an important guest of mine.

91
00:05:01,190 --> 00:05:02,390
He has come to Jiangcheng

92
00:05:02,390 --> 00:05:03,800
in search of a business partner.

93
00:05:04,270 --> 00:05:05,070
He'll be staying in our residence for now.

94
00:05:05,510 --> 00:05:07,600
Make sure that he has a comfortable stay.

95
00:05:07,750 --> 00:05:08,870
-Yes.
-Yes.

96
00:05:12,070 --> 00:05:12,600
Young Master Tang,

97
00:05:13,870 --> 00:05:14,830
to tell you the truth,

98
00:05:15,120 --> 00:05:16,310
you look like

99
00:05:16,310 --> 00:05:18,240
my younger brother very much.

100
00:05:18,750 --> 00:05:20,360
That's why everyone was confused for a moment.

101
00:05:20,560 --> 00:05:22,630
Please don't take it to heart.

102
00:05:24,560 --> 00:05:25,390
It's fine.

103
00:05:26,120 --> 00:05:26,870
Mr. Mu,

104
00:05:27,800 --> 00:05:29,160
are you not going to give me a tour

105
00:05:29,480 --> 00:05:30,560
around your grand residence?

106
00:05:31,830 --> 00:05:32,430
Of course.

107
00:05:32,680 --> 00:05:33,560
This way, please.

108
00:05:36,920 --> 00:05:38,560
(If you really are Mu Anhe,)

109
00:05:38,560 --> 00:05:39,920
(and you came back for revenge…)

110
00:05:41,120 --> 00:05:43,120
(I killed you once.)

111
00:05:43,560 --> 00:05:45,630
(I can kill you again.)

112
00:05:56,270 --> 00:05:57,720
What's this?

113
00:06:00,160 --> 00:06:01,070
Sorry, Madam.

114
00:06:01,070 --> 00:06:02,430
I was repairing the wall.

115
00:06:02,430 --> 00:06:02,950
I didn't notice you.

116
00:06:03,000 --> 00:06:03,750
I'm so sorry.

117
00:06:06,270 --> 00:06:06,680
Never mind.

118
00:06:07,390 --> 00:06:08,560
I'll just wash it off.

119
00:06:11,920 --> 00:06:12,510
What?

120
00:06:13,270 --> 00:06:14,720
The bath is being repaired right now?

121
00:06:14,870 --> 00:06:15,920
Please give me more time.

122
00:06:16,070 --> 00:06:16,870
It will be fixed soon,

123
00:06:17,360 --> 00:06:18,270
but it can't be used right away.

124
00:06:18,680 --> 00:06:19,390
If you're in a hurry,

125
00:06:19,720 --> 00:06:21,000
please use another bath elsewhere.

126
00:06:23,830 --> 00:06:26,120
Forget it. I'll use the bath in Anhe's room.

127
00:06:26,870 --> 00:06:27,430
Tell He

128
00:06:27,430 --> 00:06:29,160
to send a change of clothes there.

129
00:06:29,680 --> 00:06:30,190
Understood.

130
00:06:59,390 --> 00:07:00,240
Anhe?

131
00:07:09,660 --> 00:07:11,820
♪The tangle of love and hate between us♪

132
00:07:12,060 --> 00:07:15,420
♪Caused me to regret it♪

133
00:07:16,780 --> 00:07:21,620
♪I'm afraid we can't change our fate in this life♪

134
00:07:22,940 --> 00:07:25,780
♪I do not fear. I do not hide♪

135
00:07:26,380 --> 00:07:29,260
♪I can no longer bear the pain♪

136
00:07:29,820 --> 00:07:36,460
♪It grows as time passes♪

137
00:07:37,060 --> 00:07:38,700
♪Time will not tell you♪

138
00:07:39,140 --> 00:07:40,740
♪That I have been missing you♪

139
00:07:41,060 --> 00:07:43,500
♪You are all I think about♪

140
00:07:44,140 --> 00:07:45,460
♪No matter♪

141
00:07:45,620 --> 00:07:46,900
♪How harshly♪

142
00:07:46,900 --> 00:07:50,580
♪Life treats me♪

143
00:07:51,220 --> 00:07:52,620
♪I can only let go of my hate♪

144
00:07:52,820 --> 00:07:54,340
♪Not my love♪

145
00:07:54,820 --> 00:07:58,220
♪We promised each other life-long love♪

146
00:07:58,500 --> 00:08:04,700
♪Hopefully, we will keep that promise♪
